title: SEM_DMSO_48h
treatment_protocol_ch1: 5 µM CX-4945, 0.1 µM DEC, combination or 5 µM DMSO for 48 h.
growth_protocol_ch1: Maintained at 37°C and 5% CO2; cultured in Iscoves Medium supplemented with 10% heat-inactivated FCS and 1% penicillin/streptomycin; split every 3-4 days and seeded in a density of 3x10E5 cells per mL.
extract_protocol_ch1: Macherey-Nagel Nucleo Spin Tissue DNA extraction kit; peqGOLD bisulfite conversion kit.
hyb_protocol: Bisulfite-converted DNA was amplified, fragmented and hybridised to Illumina Infinium Human MethylationEPIC BeadChip using standard Illumina protocol.
scan_protocol: Arrays were imaged using BeadArray Reader using standard recommended Illumina scanner setting.
data_processing: The data were normalised for red and green channel separately using quantile normalisation with BeadStudio software v3.2.
